items.name: Sexy Wedding Short Dress
items.description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Training settings:

39 images, 15 steps, 14 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.


Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.3-0.7 (0.4 best results in my experiments)

  • Keys: SWSD, FLWR, NOFLWR, back view, inside church

Keywords:

  • SWSD is the main keywords, necessary, always use it, might be necessary to use a weight 1.3-1.5. It stands for Sexy Wedding Short Dress

  • FLWR is an optional keyword, might need to use a weight on it 1.2-1.7. It stands for Flower and by using it you will end with a dress with many flower decorations.

  • NOFLWR it's the opposite of FLWR but doesn't always work, might need a bigger weight

  • back view, inside church these are self explanatory.

Also, you might want a not white dress, in this case you can add stuff like "red dress" or "black dress".

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians

items.name: LoRA Peace Sign✌
items.description:
LoRA Peace Sign✌

This is LoRA, designed to increase the accuracy of drawing the peace sign.

Usage

  • Use the AUTOMATIC1111's [stable-diffusion-webui](https://github.com/AUTOMATIC1111/stable-diffusion-webui.git).

  • Install the latest version of the [sd-webui-additional-networks](https://github.com/kohya-ss/sd-webui-additional-networks.git) extension from its URL in the "Extensions" tab on the Web UI.

  • Copy the LoRA file to the "stable-diffusion-webui/extensions/sd-webui-additional-networks/models/lora" folder.

  • Select the LoRA file and click "Send to * number" in the "Additional Networks" tab on the Web UI.

  • In the "txt2img" or "img2img" tab, enable the 'Additional Networks' option, verify the LoRA name, and adjust the weight as needed.

  • Select the SD 1.5 model as Stable Diffusion checkpoint.

License

LoRA Peace Sign under the [CreativeML Open RAIL-M](https://huggingface.co/spaces/CompVis/stable-diffusion-license). If any derivative of this model is made, please share your changes accordingly.

items.name: Squatting Double Penetration
items.description:
This is my first sex position LoRA and took me way to much time. All training images were also generated using SD, since the pose is really hard to find via regular search.

Be sure to use: clip skip 2, highres.fix (0.25-0.35, ~25steps)

Always add: <lora:Squat_Suck_18:0.8>, squatting, 1boy, vaginal,

I suggest using 0.6-0.8 as the LoRA weight.

Since all training images were generated, the style likes to bleed through when going higher. Also likes to sometimes delete the guys back leg. It works really well with style LoRAs.

The following things can be changed fairly well via additional tags:

anal: replace "vaginal" with "anal"

deepthroat: add "deepthroat", more weight = deeper

irrumatio: add "irrumatio, hand on anothers head"

You can also roll the finger lottery and add "holding penis" to the prompt (don't combine with "deepthroat"). If you get lucky you can get her to hold the penis, but this is fairly inconsistent.

If you get a perfect picture but the face is still somehow messed up my trick is to use "LottaLewds" BallsDeep LoRA via inpaint. To do this:

  • inpaint the entire face + the tip of penis entering the mouth (not the hair)

  • chose: inpaint marked, original, only masked, 0.55-0.65 denoise

  • use the basic prompt for your character, while removing things that define the body

  • add: <lora:lottalewdsBallsDeep_v1:1>, from side, sloppy blowjob, blowjob face, cum in mouth,

Tips:

  • You can remove remnants of fingers on the penis by adding "arms behind back"

  • make sure you do not have facial expressions like "smile", "grin" in your prompt

The LoRA was trained on 27 pictures (i went thought at least 200 until settling on these) in anything v3, and the images were all generated on AOM2/orangemix vae and were not inpainted at all.

You can help to improve this model by posting good pictures using the pose on this page. The things that'd help me most with advancing it would be entirely different styles, pictures where the guys back leg is very clearly visible and good pictures of the girl holding the penis.

My character prompts also all include: "beautiful, masterpiece, best quality, extremely detailed face, perfect lighting, 1girl, solo", so if it doesn't quite get there for you try adding some of these.

*all depicted characters are above the age of 18.

items.name: Fantasy - AutoPrompt - Awesome prompt lists
items.description:
A brand new pack of fantasy themed prompt wildcard lists. This was a fun creation. Prompts such as these really shows the strength of creativity coupled with the wild results from stable diffusion models.

Fantasy landscapes, castles, architecture, magical creatures, cozy fantasy, cute fantasy. Lots of possibilities of creating a little magic with this pack!

(⚠️Be aware the due the the nature of the model you are using, the prompt lists cozy_fantasy_creatures / cute_fantasy_creatures might produce some weird outputs. Adjust the promptlists by removing the word/words creating weird things. You can also comment here if some of the items produce weird things. I have removed lots of words and tested a few hundred generations.)

Example prompts from category - fantasy

  • Example prompt for castle_lotr_landscape: moonstone rococo castle, obsidian turrets, troll, unicorn, A dramatic sunset casting vibrant hues over a range of rugged mountains

  • Example prompt for castle_scifi_landscape: moonstone rococo castle, obsidian turrets, troll, unicorn, Giant space station

  • Example prompt for castle_landscape: moonstone rococo castle, obsidian turrets, troll, unicorn, a dramatic cliffside overlooking the ocean

  • Example prompt for fantasy_architecture: renaissance oil painting, tree-top village, pool light, artificial light

  • Example prompt for painters_fantasy_architecture: Create a magnificent, ultra-detailed illustration, Johannes Vermeer, tree-top village

  • Example prompt for fantasy_fantastical_architecture: renaissance oil painting, fey, tree-top village, pool light, artificial light

  • Example prompt for magical_creatures: Create a magnificent, ultra-detailed illustration, fey, troll, unicorn, a dramatic cliffside overlooking the ocean

  • Example prompt for magical_creatures_portrait: portrait, fey, troll, unicorn, with a swamp in the background

  • Example prompt for magical_creatures_in_a_container: fey, troll, unicorn, in an ecosphere

  • Example prompt for alchemy_in_a_container: fey, Brewing a magical stew, in an ecosphere

  • Example prompt for cozy_alchemy: Alchemist with a crystal ball, fey, Brewing a magical stew, A rustic apothecary with shelves full of colorful herbs and jars of mysterious powders

  • Example prompt for cozy_fantasy_creatures: fey, Tiny, lovable unicorns with shimmering, rainbow manes, Darling, tiny gnomes with colorful hats and bushy beards, Whimsical, petite wyverns with sparkling wings and gentle smiles, with a swamp in the background

Usage

  1. Open automatic1111 SD / any other SD creation tool with similar prompt file input

  2. Select <Script> --> Prompts from file or textbox

  3. Drop file or copy paste contents in the "List of prompts inputs"

  4. To view information on images you have created you can use "PNG Info" tab in Automatic1111.

items.name: Disoptics
items.description:
How to use

To use it, you need to register <lora:disoptics_yiu_v12:0.85> in the prompt field. I recommend exactly this value of the LoRA weight, as it gives more variability.

It is recommended to write the following tokens: design, glass lines, CIFilters, distortion, refraction, simple composition.

Copy the prompta and parameters from the preview to this model — you will not lose.

What the model is suitable for

This model is needed to simulate forced displacement and refraction of light. She copes well with the tokens "man, "woman" and abstract objects.

I trained LoRA on the Deliberate_v2 model, so it's better to work with her in pairs.

Which model works best with

It is best to use the Deliberate_v2 model.

I made this as a test, then decided to upload it. I used 14 game screenshots, improved using IMG2IMG. This same method should work for other Genshin NPCs and environments.

Recommended weight （おすすめウエイト）:

0.7-0.9 for Default outfit. デフォルト衣装なら0.7-0.9です。

Around 0.4 for completely different outfits. 別衣装に代わりたいなら0.4ぐらいです。

You may need to use the recommended tags at lower weights.

低いウエイトの場合、おすすめタグをもっと使う必要になるかもです。

See gallery tags for examples of how to change her outfit.

衣装の代わり方はギャラリーの画像のタグを見てください。

Recommended tags (おすすめタグ）:

1girl, high ponytail, brown eyes, long sleeves, high heels, accessory, black pantyhose, short hair

Use these if she appears incorrectly, or if you're using low weight.

items.name: Chun Li LoRA
items.description:
This is my second-ish attempt at making a LoRA, so constructive criticism is appreciated.

Trained on altogether way too many images (around 1700) This gives you an accurate Chun every time. Works great with any model and any style LoRA at 1 weight, but it was trained on a lot of hentai, so you may have trouble with nipples and cameltoe showing through.

I tried adding trigger words for Chun's different outfits, but they didn't work so well. If you're looking to make a specific Chun costume, there are tags you can input that you can see in the image examples. In general, they are:

Good General Tags: brown hair, wide hips, thick thighs, muscular female, kicking, fighting stance, perfect brown eyes with white sclera, flexible

SF2 Chun (Chun Classic): chinese clothing, blue dress, double bun, pelvic curtain, pantyhose, bun cover, puffy short sleeves, sash, white footwear,

SFA Chun (Fortnite Chun): blue vest, unitard, blue pants, skintight, yellow ribbon, short hair, sneakers, bare shoulders (Gets the best look without Wide Hips and Thick Thighs tags)

SF5 Chun (No-Bun Chun): chinese clothing, black dress, gold trim, pelvic curtain, ponytail, double braid, long hair, cleavage (This is the least consistent one, you may want to put Pantyhose in the negative tags)

SF6 Chun (Aul Lady Chun): mature female, makeup, yellow ribbon, chinese clothing, cleavage cutout, white shirt, tight pants, blue pants (Looks more accurate without the Muscular Female tag, you may want to put Unitard in the negative tags so as to not confuse it with SFA's costume)

items.name: Narita Top Road (umamusume)
items.description:
LoHa of Narita Top Road (umamusume). Please install extension on WebUI.

After installing extension, put LoHa file in your sd/models/lora folder and write LoRA notation in prompt to applying LoHa. <lora:loha_name:weight>

All uploaded images are generated by AOM3A1

All of my works is free. If you'd like to support me, feel free to buy me a coffee. 👍

Recommended options

  • LoRA weight 0.7 ~ 0.8

  • Trigger words

    • Base

      • narita top road \(umamusume\)

    • Racing competition costume :

      • ear cover, star hair ornament, brooch, sleeveless dress, purple dress, white bow, mismatched gloves, white gloves, black gloves, shoulder cutout, puffy long sleeves, detached sleeves, see-through sleeves, frills, shorts under dress, short shorts, purple shorts, thigh strap, knee boots, purple footwear

    • Tracen summer uniform :

      • tracen school uniform, summer uniform, serafuku, puffy short sleeves, purple bowtie, horseshoe ornament, sailor collar, sailor shirt, purple shirt, white skirt, pleated skirt, frilled skirt, miniskirt, zettai ryouiki, white thighhighs, brown footwear, loafers

    • Tracen winter uniform :

      • tracen school uniform, winter uniform, puffy long sleeves, sailor collar, sailor shirt, purple shirt, white bowtie, horseshoe ornament, purple skirt, frills, brown footwear, loafers

Use a model derived from or mixed with animefull model.

  • Settings

    • Stable Diffusion WebUI by Automatic1111

    • DPM++ Series(SDE Karras, 2M Karras, etc.)

    • about 20 steps, CFG scale 3.5~6.5

    • I recommend kl-f8-anime2.vae

    • CLIP skip = 1

    • Use Hires.fix to get higher quality image

      • Upscaler

        • Latent, Latent (nearest-exact), Latent (bicubic antialiased) or other Latent series.

      • Denoising strength 0.50~0.65

LoRA training info

  • trained on sd-scripts by kohya_ss.

    • LyCORIS by KohakuBlueleaf

    • Thank you all a lot!

  • based on Animefull-pruned model

  • 86 images consist of

    • 4x low quality 34 images

    • 8x medium quality 21 images

    • 16x high quality 31 images

    • => 1 epoch = 800 images

  • replaced character feature tags with narita top road \(umamusume\)

    • 1girl, multicolored eyes, bangs, horse tail, simple background, brown eyes, horse girl, yellow eyes, tail, symbol in eye, orange eyes, parted bangs, purple eyes, blonde hair, pink hair, medium hair, solo, long hair, multicolored hair, streaked hair, short hair, animal ears, white hair, horse ears, pink eyes, light brown hair, red eyes, brown hair

    • I think these tags are the essentials of Narita Top Road or

    • unnecessary for training because of duplication.

  • resolution : 768x768 with aspect ratio bucketing.

  • other training settings is included in training_data.zip or metadata of LoRA file.

And, special thanks to my best friend. DH.

items.description:
Proudly exhibiting his newly captured meat shield, just recently strapped on his armor, our monstrous humanoid decides he might as well have some fun along the way...

Trained on Anything v3 - so I guess it will work best with models using booru - style tags.

Activation words: onarmor, meat shield, fanny packing. I recommend Clip Skip 2.

"onarmor" was chosen in an attempt, not to weaken "real" tags, but I guess I don't fully understand, how Lora-learning works, so this might have been the wrong approach.

Depending on the model, you might want to give more weigth to the activation words (onarmor:1.2), (fanny packing:1.2)

The lora mostly delivers the pose. To acutally see some action, add some "sex" activities, bodily fluids, and see what SD makes of it...

If you happen to use "meat shield" in the prompt and literally stumble across pieces of "meat" in the output, I guess I this is either because I didn't really "get" how activation words work, or that my Lora is incompatible with the used checkpoint/model.

My first Lora. Grabbed a whole bunch of images from the 'boorus and gave it a go. Next time, I guess, I'll try less pictures, but better quality/curation?

items.description:
LoRA for the character Ai Hoshino from the anime Oshi No Ko.

Leave a rating if you like it, and post your feedback and pictures!

Trained on NAI with multiple passes / resolutions to better capture the eye details. Should work on most anime models. My images were generated using AnyLora.

How to use:

  • Weight 1.0 with your usual CFG. Use hires fix for final image.

  • Trigger word: hoshino ai

  • Outfits tags: star dress, frilled dress, ascot dress

  • Accessories tags: rabbit hair accessory, star hair ornament (these should already be associated with the outfits; but add to positive prompt if missing, or to negative to remove it)

If an image generation is missing a detail of the outfit, simply describe it in the prompt. E.g. the skirt in the ascot dress is white, just add pink skirt; the outfit is missing thighhighs, just add that in; etc. See the prompts in my example images for reference.

Some details may not work 100% of the time as the data available may not still be sufficient to fully generalize the concepts. I may revisit this one once more data (e.g. episodes and fan art) becomes available.

Additional info

I make these models for fun and for the challenge and release them for free for everyone to enjoy, for non-commercial use (see license). The one thing I ask of you is to provide rating and feedback! That helps me understand where I can improve and helps me stay motivated to produce more content!

I accept suggestions or requests here or on Civitai discord server.

You can also check my more polished images and upcoming models on my pixiv profile.

https://ko-fi.com/gorillamonsooniii

https://www.patreon.com/GorillaMonsoon

Solstice

Solstice is my attempt to create Manhwa (korean webtoon) artsyle model. Different from the usual manga art style used in some of the models trained in stable diffusion.

Legal & Risk

In principle, I do not support the use of this model to generate any adult content. When using this model, users must abide by laws and regulations, and do not infringe other people's reputation, privacy or portrait rights.

Changelogs

  • v1.0-Areum: First release, "forking" my Eclipse checkpoint, reworked most of it's datasets to Manhwa artstyle.

  • v1.0-Areum: added safetensors format, eveything is same as ckpt format, just in safetensors format

  • v1.0-Areum-NoEMA-fp16: added Pruned, No EMA, fp16 version. need download my GMIII VAE, you can use any other VAE, but the result may vary.

Who find this model perfect

  • LoRA/LoCon/LyCORIS user who are looking for a compatible checkpoint

  • Creative prompters

  • People who needs Manhwa model

Usage

  • Almost compatible with all sampling methods available, but Euler a and DPM++ SDE Karras are my recommendation

  • Use 20-40 sampling steps, more than 40 is not giving any improvement

  • CFG: 4.5-7

  • Less complicated, short negative prompts are better

  • This model include VAE, so please use with it.

If using Hires:

  • Hires step: 10-20 steps

  • R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6b, if you're prefer Latent upscaler, use Latent (nearest-exact)

After download this model, try to share with us about your findings.

Please give star reviews with your generated picture if you like it.

I'm also accept commisioning for LoRA/Ckpt

items.name: 【Art Style】Nanoless Style
items.description:
2023/7/5 update

Update dataset. Retrain the model using new craft.

Introduction

A LoRA model trained with ~500 images by Nanoless. No trigger tag. The 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) are recommended. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version (original) YesMix.

Cautions (Must Read)

  • Some preview images are generated using 'Hires Fix' and upscaled using 'SD Upscale'. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

  • The maximum of generating resolution should not exceed 1024 theoretically, otherwise extra/deformed head/limbs will be waiting for you :). Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

items.name: Meiya Mitsurugi (Alternative VN) - Muv-Luv Alternative
items.description:
Huh? I never expected my first SFW LORA to be from Muv-Luv. And not for a lack of trying I simply didn't find any good doujins and the sex scenes from the visual novel are a bit lacking. So here's it is, finally a SFW LORA from me ...I feel a bit dirty actually. Hopefully it is flexible enough to produce NSFW or I'll be very disappointed.

Anyway... I trained this almost exclusively on the Muv-Luv alternative original art. I saw some of the anime screenshots and my eyes bled quite badly. So I am going to keep postponing watching it until I get enough mental strength to handle the disappointment.

V2

Finally took my time to retrain this and oh boy was it a pain. Similar complex outfits in different colors are a pain to train due to bleedover. In this case the TSF pilot suits were a pain. I had to do a bunch of iterations and even now it isn't perfect but it seems to correctly set the colors at least 60% of the time and the rest the colors are only a bit shifted so good enough i say.

Got good results with: <lora:MitsurugiMeiyaV2:0.7> mitsurugimeiya,

Available tagged outfits are:

  • School_uniform_White_shirt_White_skirt_Purple_bowtie_Black_pantyhose_Black_boots_Black_turtleneck: Hakuryou school uniform Meiya version (She uses a black turtleneck undershirt it seems.)

  • see-through_bodysuit: Not really see through but the white and tan version which was made for cadets to loose their shame(that was the in game reason.) SD refused to make it the correct color and tagging it like this gave me the most stable repetitions.

  • TSFSuitBlackWhite: White frame with a black core, colors may shift sometimes.

  • TSFSuitBlueBlack: Black frame with a blue core, colors may shift sometimes.

  • Black_sweater_Blue_skirt_Black_pantyhose_Black_shoes: her casual outfit.

  • Black_sweater_Black_skirt_Black_thighhighs: a variation of her casual outfit but with a black skirt.

  • Gray_military_uniform_Gray_skirt_Gray_pantyhose_Black_boots: Meiya's officer uniform.

No dataset this time as i used a bunch of the game assets so only the tags summary.

V1 and 1.1

I got ok-ish results with: <lora:MitsurugiMeiya:0.7>, MitsurugiMeiya, solo, hair_ribbon,

As the Dataset was relatively easy to gather and process, I spent most of my efforts with her outfits. Her available outfits should be(Got some contamination between her TSF suits variants might need to add color description to get it to be right.):

  • HakuryouHiiragiUniform

  • TSFSuitWhiteBlack

  • TSFSuitWhite

  • TSFSuitBlack

  • TSFSuitBlackWhite

  • MilitaryUniform (generic grunt uniform from the boot camp should have a sleeveless shirt variation and a jacket one.)

  • OfficerSuit (add skirt_suit or she might get pants)

  • BlackSweaterBlueSkirt (Some casual outfit she uses)

I'll be adding the tag summary in place of the training data, as the training set is mostly Game CG I won't be adding it. Age, please don't sue me.

Please buy the games and support the original creators. ...but remember to play it in order! Do so regardless of if Extra is a bit painful. The muv-luv games are just that good, probably above the fate franchise.

Note: I finally did get to testing it for making NSFW, it works fine as long as you use some good position TI or LORA. I recommend corneo's (corneo_cowgirl:.9).

items.name: Yui with origin outfit (Princess Connect!)
items.description:
This model is trained as Yui, a character from Princess Connect! with her original outfit. It's based on SD1.5 model, it would competiable with other checkpoints based on SD1.5. Safe to blend with other LoRA, LoCon based on SD1.5 as well.

Triggered with "yui, origin" for character appearance

Add "short hair, pleated skirt, puffy sleeves, red skirt, thigh boots, thighhighs, white footwear, yui \(princess_connect!\)", for fully lock down details of the character with her origin outfit.

Suggested weight 0.8-1.0, works fine with 0.9.

Tested with Chilloutmix Ni, Anything 4.5, AOM3A3, CounterfeitV25, meinamix_meinaV8, perfectWorld_v2Baked, neverendingDreamNED_bakedVae, check the samples for details (Hires Fix with latent should be used with caution, use 4x-Ultrasharp in Extras insdead).

It's not trained to change to other outfits, still it's possible, lower the weights while enhance the alternative outfit description, see the samples for ref.

**It's a quick cook, but should be stable enough to use, play with the prompts and have fun. :)
